  • Classes in org.stringmatching.matcher used by org.stringmatching.determinist.aho_corasick 
    Class and Description
    IMatcher
    This interface define the basic function for a Matcher algorithm For an input text the doMatch function must to parse the text (stream) in order to find all the positions in the text for a pattern/s To allow concurrence by splitting the text in segments, the start position is used to set correctly the pattern position in the full text.
    Matcher
    Abstract class focused on to establish a bridge between the matching process and their outputs
